high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink in the bathroom at the end of the hall.
Pick up the alarmclock on the left side of the sink.
Turn around, go to the end of the hall and turn right, go across to the dresser.
Place the alarmclock on the left end of the dresser toward the front.
Turn around, go back to the sink at the end of the hall.
Pick up the alarmclock in the sink.
Head back to the end of the hall and turn right, go across to the dresser.
Place the alarmclock on the dresser behind the other clock.
anns.task_desc: Place two AlarmClocks on the Dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to enter into the bathroom sink.
Take the alarm clock from the left side of the faucet.
Turn your back and walk straight and turn right to enter into room and walk towards the dresser which is kept on the end of the room.
Put the alarm clock on the top left side of the dresser.
Turn back and walk out of the room and then turn left and walk straight to reach the sink in the bathroom again.
Take the alarm clock from the right side of the faucet.
Turn your back and walk straight and turn right to enter into room and walk towards the dresser again.
Put the alarm clock on the top left side of the dresser next to the first alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Put the AlarmClock on the top left side of the Dresser.
